  ('social-worker-moex-01951', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-107-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '某社區針對428位老人，全面進行福利需求調查，結果發現有85位（20%）受訪者，自認健康不佳。試 問受訪者所反應的是下列那一項需求？', '["表達性需求（expressed need）", "感受性需求（perceived need）", "規範性需求（normative need）", "相對性需求（relative need）"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:11+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "f80e8558d678", "answer_pdf_sha1": "ce4f756709e0", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "107030", "c": "107", "s": "0603", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "107", "exam_name": "107年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 15, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-01952', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-107-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '在社會服務方案規劃設定過程目標時，下列何者不屬於稽核點的概念？', '["聘僱個案管理員", "服務對象完成職業訓練，並取得證書", "完成一份期中報告", "將設計一套個案篩選系統"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:11+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "f80e8558d678", "answer_pdf_sha1": "ce4f756709e0", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "107030", "c": "107", "s": "0603", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "107", "exam_name": "107年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 16, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
